strings: <voice_0x01001467><se_high>to paradise in eden: Thank you so much, the Cuban Council must have brought him here.
<voice_0x01001468><se_high>to paradise in eden: The only way to stop Dark Lord Rapthorne's awakening is to seal the scepter and lock it in...
<voice_0x01001469><se_high>to paradise in eden: We will do our best to help you.
<voice_0x0100146A><se_high>to paradise in eden: you are here
<voice_0x0100146C><se_high>to paradise in eden: I ask these people to bring their precious goods to Cuba. Can you tell security?
<voice_0x0100146E><se_high>to paradise in eden: As you know, I want to talk about the Modular Rural Development Department.
<voice_0x0100146F><se_high>to paradise in eden: It belongs to the cabbage family and was given this name because of its thick leaves. There is a huge leaf in the world of darkness.
<voice_0x01001470><se_high>to paradise in eden: They say that if you mark it on the map, you will immediately see a great evil.
<voice_0x01001471><se_high>to paradise in eden: The fate of the world lies in your hands. We all believe in you and wish you every success.
